Captions for standard pillow comparison video
Describes the visual demonstration of a standard pillow losing shape over time

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
[A standard pillow is shown from the side]

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:06.000
[Weight is applied to simulate head pressure]

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:09.000
[The pillow compresses and flattens significantly]

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:12.000
[The filling shifts unevenly to the sides]

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:15.000
[The pillow fails to bounce back to its original shape]

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:18.000
[Visible loss of loft and support structure]

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:21.000
[The pillow remains flat and misshapen]

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:24.000
[Demonstration shows inconsistent support]

